---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 331
  - Title: Shekel Hakodesh
    Location: 151
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
---
If Destiny will that fortune smile upon thee, it will come to thee,
though thou art far away; or if it be ills thou’rt destined to bear,
thou canst not elude them, though thou be borne to the skies.
